		<text oae-label="Text" oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="25">
			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Help yourself to some noodles."/> 
<b>B:</b>	Thanks, but I'll pass on the noodles.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Don't you eat noodles?"/> 
<b>B:</b>	I do, but I'm allergic to peanut sauce.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="I'm sorry.  I didn't know that.  Didn't you use to eat peanuts?"/>  
<b>B:</b>	Yes, I did.  But not anymore. Don't worry about it.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="How about some garlic bread?"/> 
<b>B:</b>	Thank you. I'm crazy about garlic bread. And I’m a big salad eater.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Oh, good.  There's a lot of salad."/>]]>
		</text>

