<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Mmm.  The chicken smells terrific."/> 
<b>A:</b>	Actually, it's not chicken.  It's steak.
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Oh, then I think I'll pass."/>
<b>A:</b>	Don't you like steak?
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="To tell you the truth, I'm not much of a steak eater."/> 
<b>A:</b>	Why don't you have some fish then?
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Great. I love seafood!"/> 
<b>A:</b>	Would you like some soda?
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Soda doesn't agree with me.  Could I just have some water?"/>
